727996f-a.title: Queens: South Road - Waltham Street
727996f-a.text:
South Road, north side, east from Waltham: Street, across
Sutphin Boulevard. The frame houses on the left are on Sutnhin
Boulevard, which was formely known, at this point,as Jay Street.
P. L. Sperr  March 30, 1932
